    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's been my absolute pride and joy, and I've kept it in pristine, showroom condition. It drives like a dream and looks like it just rolled off the lot! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
