    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it still has that fresh, perfect feel inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
